  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nCurrently if fetching messages fails due to a faulty store node then the loading indicator disappears making the user thinking the fetching is done. Behind the scenes another store node is tried and messages are eventually and suddenly loaded. We should continue to show the loading indicator so the user knows that the app is still trying to fetch messages.\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\nWhen opening the app and a message fetch fails due to some store node issues, the loading indicator continues to show until the messages are fetched. ideally we show some sort of message that the fetching failed and another node is being tried.\r\n",
